Animated view/zoom scale cache
==============================

Date: 2026-07-02

Purpose
-------
Avoid repeated animation lag when switching back to a zoom/fit/view size that
has already been generated once.

Previously, FreeImage.resize() always created a fresh scaled AnimatedImage
wrapper. That meant every return to the same fit or zoom level could rebuild and
preload scaled frames again. This was especially noticeable on large GIFs.

This change adds a per-image cache for animated scaled views.

